{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_07_02",
  "title": "LizNoir 07 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一週間後　決勝トーナメント前夜祭",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One week later‚ eve of the final tournament",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "私達LizNoirが決勝トーナメントに進めたことを\n大変嬉しく思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am very happy that we LizNoir\nwere able to get to the final tournament.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.533333389,
      "endTime": 8.2256235044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4999999921
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そして、宣言させて下さい\n私達は、必ず優勝してBIG4入りを果たします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ please allow me to make a declaration\nWe will definitely win and achieve our goal of becoming BIG4!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4999999921,
      "endTime": 16.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7466.666674600001,
          "startTime": 15.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0666671674
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "応援、よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We‚ look forward to your support!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0666671674,
      "endTime": 19.382587091199998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころの最高のアイドルスマイル\n受け止めて下さいね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please accept\nKokoro's best idol smile~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5666686933,
      "endTime": 24.6333332062,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3699.9969561000016,
          "startTime": 23.2666656494
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0000014624
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0000014624
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.2333340329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "結局、葵は参加を保留したまま、三人だけで挨拶か……\n予選はなんとか突破出来たが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ Aoi remains on hold‚ and they'll greeted just three members…\nWe managed to get through the preliminary rounds…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.100003044,
      "endTime": 35.7095724029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0000015181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "三人体制のまま勝ち上がれるほど\n決勝トーナメントは甘くなさそうだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Final tournament doesn't seem easy enough\nto win with just three members…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0000015181,
      "endTime": 41.320931331500006,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5666.666611000003,
          "startTime": 41.6666681291
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5666681291
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、葵抜きのLizNoirなら\n確実に私達が勝ちます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ if it's LizNoir without Aoi‚\nwe will surely win",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1000005008,
      "endTime": 49.1300911189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依……\nこの後はトリエルの出番だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui…\nNext was TRINITYAiLE's turn",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3333338341,
      "endTime": 52.9032658657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1000005008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。優とすみれはスケジュールが合いませんでしたが\nせめて、私だけでも参加をと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Yu and Sumire's schedules didn't match up‚\nAt least‚ I thought I should participate",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1000005008,
      "endTime": 59.825170445599994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったな\nでも前夜祭だし、無理に出なくても良かったんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see\nBut it's just eve‚ you didn't have to push yourself to come out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0333338341,
      "endTime": 65.5846718392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.8000005008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "優のアドバイスなんです。この大会はAI判定に加えて\n視聴者の投票も加算されて勝敗が決まるルールですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was Yu's advice. This tournament's rules are based on AI judging as well as\naudience votes‚ which are added to decide win and lose",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8000005008,
      "endTime": 74.9547854664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "出来るだけ印象を残しておいた方が有利です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's better to leave as good an impression as possible",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1666671675,
      "endTime": 78.2234477919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4333343428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "抜け目ないな……トリエルは優勝候補筆頭なのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're really on the ball… Even though TRINITYAiLE is leading candidate for the championship…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4333343428,
      "endTime": 83.0445816916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスが出ませんからね\n……彼女達は、どうして出ないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's because ⅢX isn't participating\n…Why aren't they participating?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2333343428,
      "endTime": 89.5596609991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "「空席狙いなんてダサい真似はしたくない」だってさ\n……良くも悪くも、彼女達らしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said‚ 'We don't want to do something lame like aiming for a empty seat'\n…For better or for worse‚ that's just like them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7666676761,
      "endTime": 97.28199636949999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか。でも、スリクスがいてもいなくても\n私達はBIG4を目指して、全力を尽くすだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. But whether ⅢX is here or not‚\nwe just have to aim for BIG4 and give it our all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4666676761,
      "endTime": 106.6996834995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7117074094
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.9666666588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、葵は本当にこの大会に出ないんですか？\n出来れば、万全の状態のリズノワと戦いたいんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ is Aoi really not going to participate in this tournament?\nIf possible‚ I'd like to fight LizNoir when they are in perfect condition",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9666666588,
      "endTime": 115.8524715981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.0666666588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……分からない\nLizNoirが抱える問題が解決しないことにはな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't know that\nIf the problem LizNoir is facing is not solved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0666666588,
      "endTime": 121.201405867,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14333.331433799984,
          "startTime": 130.3999980926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか。解決することを私も願っています\nそろそろ出番なので、行ってきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is that so. I hope it gets resolved‚ too\nMy turn is coming up soon‚ so I'll be going now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3999999922,
      "endTime": 129.8999980926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルは準備万端って感じだな……\nだけど、リズノワは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE seems to be fully prepared…\nBut as for LizNoir――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9666707278,
      "endTime": 137.8722715617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7633.32736480001,
          "startTime": 139.5999980926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.9666647593
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.9666647593
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.5666707278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、瑠依さん、お疲れ様です！\nトリエルも決勝トーナメント進出おめでとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rui-san‚ thank you for your effort!\nCongratulations to TRINITYAiLE for advancing to the final tournament‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5666707278,
      "endTime": 147.0728837252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
