      "text": "ふふっ、こころの言う通りよ、愛\n私達、BIG4の座を譲るつもりは少しもないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ Kokoro is right‚ Ai\nWe have no intention of giving up our seat in the BIG4‚ not even a little",
