      "text": "当然ね。同じ事務所でも、ライブバトルになれば\nそんなこと関係ないわ。全力で戦うだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Even if we're in the same agency‚ in a live battle‚\nthat kind of thing doesn't matter. We'll just fight with all our might",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.3000040611,
      "endTime": 172.6297777733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
