      "text": "以前一度だけ、対戦させていただいたことがあるんです\nあの時は事務所の者が、みなさんに酷いことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We once had a match against each other\nAt that time‚ a member of our agency did something terrible to everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
