      "text": "……そういえば、そんな人がいたような気がする\nそっか、あの時君と対戦したのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Come to think of it‚ I think there was someone like that\nThat's it‚ I had a match against you back then",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.8333740157,
      "endTime": 275.91990451040004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
