      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 276.1333740157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。その節は、大変ご迷惑をお掛けしました\nあれは、彼が単独でやったことですので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes. Back then‚ I'm truly sorry for the trouble we caused\nThat was something he did on his own‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 276.1333740157,
      "endTime": 287.1200304907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
