      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいよ。言われるまで忘れてたし\nそもそも君が悪いんじゃないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. I had forgotten until you mentioned it\nBesides‚ it wasn't your fault",
