      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran005.m4a",
      "text": "そう言っていただけると、私も少し気が楽になります\n私、リズノワのみなさん、特に葵さんを尊敬してるので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing you say that makes me feel a bit relieved\nI‚ respect everyone in LizNoir‚ especially you‚ Aoi-san",
