      "text": "僕を尊敬なんて、物好きだな\n莉央の方が、アイドルとしてずっといいお手本になるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To respect me‚ you are strange\nRio would make a much better idol role model",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.7000650963,
      "endTime": 311.94033742759996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、莉央さんも素敵だと思います\nでも私、葵さんのダンスが一番好きなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I think Rio-san is wonderful‚ too\nBut for me‚ I like Aoi-san's dancing the best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.1333984297,
      "endTime": 320.6533924978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 320.8667256595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕は好きなことを好きにやってるだけだよ\n……協調性がないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just doing what I like‚ how I like it\n…I'm not cooperative",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.8667256595,
      "endTime": 327.259399438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 327.4667012454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それが葵さんのダンスの個性です\n葵さんが纏う自由な空気が、私大好きなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that is the color of Aoi-san's dancing\nI love the free atmosphere that Aoi-san exudes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.4667012454,
      "endTime": 336.89998792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、私もこの大会に出場してるんですよ\n前夜祭はサボっちゃいましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I'm also participating in this tournament\nAlthough I skipped the eve festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.2000610274,
      "endTime": 343.6200609129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 343.8333943606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん。そうなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm. Is that so",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.8333943606,
      "endTime": 345.9907866717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran009.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、決勝トーナメントでは\n葵さんと一緒のステージに立てるように頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ in the final tournament‚\nI will do my best to stand on the same stage as Aoi-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.2000610273,
      "endTime": 352.6534047049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 352.8667378665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "僕の出場は……約束は出来ないな、悪いけど、その\n自由なダンスっていうのが、今の僕には踊れないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My participation is… can't promise that‚ sorry‚ well‚\nfree dancing you mentioned‚ I can't dance it right now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.8667378665,
      "endTime": 363.369436574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 363.6334187747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "……自分が納得のいかないパフォーマンスを\nファンの前でこれ以上見せたくないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't want to show a performance that I'm not satisfied with\nto the fans anymore",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.6334187747,
      "endTime": 369.1535549404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran010.m4a",
      "text": "予選もお休みされていましたけど……\nお体の具合でも悪いんですか？　それかお怪我でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were absent from the preliminary rounds‚ too…\nAre you feeling unwell? Or did you get injured…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.366752108,
      "endTime": 376.9134209236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 377.1000874759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのじゃないんだ\n……ただの、不調だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not something like that\n…It's just‚ bad condition",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 377.1000874759,
      "endTime": 382.1853934527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran011.m4a",
      "text": "何か事情があるんですね。詳しくは聞きませんが\n……やっぱり、葵さんは本当のプロですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There must be some reason. I won't ask for details‚ but\n…Still‚ Aoi-san‚ you're a true professional",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 382.4000874759,
      "endTime": 392.2734007121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 392.4667337975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……どうかな。君はそんなのワガママだと思わないの？\n自分が満足出来ないからって、立たないだなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well. Don't you think that's being selfish?\nTo not go on stage just because I'm not satisfied",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 392.4667337975,
      "endTime": 401.1333354949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 401.466723625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran012.m4a",
      "text": "自分のパフォーマンスに妥協しない、葵さんの考え方\n私は尊敬します。あの……突然で失礼なんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san's way of thinking‚ not compromising on your own performance\nI respect that. Um… I know this is sudden and rude‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 401.466723625,
      "endTime": 413.9134349745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran013.m4a",
      "text": "連絡先、交換させてもらえたり……しませんか？\n私、ダンスのこと相談する相手がいなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "would you be willing to swap phone number…?\nI don't have anyone to talk to about dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 414.1001017174,
      "endTime": 425.0534329971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 425.2667663496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいよ。返事するかしないかは分からないけど\nそれで良ければ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine. I don't know if I'll reply or not\nIf it's okay though",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 425.2667663496,
      "endTime": 430.2588978689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "蘭々",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ranran",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_07_02-ranran014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n……ふふっ、今日は、最高の日です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much\n…Hehe‚ today‚ is the best day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 430.4667663496,
      "endTime": 435.3400245111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 435.5333577395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
